author: HardyHarHarHarlow
text: I wish for a magic genie so I can wish for sleep.

author: HardyHarHarHarlow
text: Hey, check my profile to see my new poem "Nothing"!! Pretty proud of it after writing it late at night 😁

author: HardyHarHarHarlow
text:
Friends have left. 
Family left you isolated and alone. 
Because you couldn't care for them while being something, so nothing will do.

author: HardyHarHarHarlow
text:
My time and energy is spent on others. 
I don't drink enough water. 
I don't get enough sleep. 
I don't have the nutrients for survival. 

But what is the point of survival when you're nothing?

author: HardyHarHarHarlow
text:
Nothing 
I care for those around me. 
My family. 
My friends. 
My family's friends. 
My friend's families. 

Strangers on the street. 
Enemies in my home. 
All so those around me are not nothing. 

But where does that leave me?
As nothing.
